{"word":"διχοτομέω","slug":"διχοτομέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διχοτομέω</el></b> [<el>δίχα, τομή</el> ‘a cutting’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <el>τέμνω</el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>διχοτόμος</el> ‘cutting in two’] <b><i>cut in two, dismember,</i></b> of a slave undergoing severe punishment <b><a href='B:470 24:51'>Mt 24:51</a>; <a href='B:490 12:46'>Lk 12:46</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διχοστασία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διψάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}